      <p>Ecological Dynamics studies human behaviour in the real world. We take off our lab coat and look at the way skill acquisition and perception works within the context that we find ourselves in on a daily basis.</p>
      <p>We take into consideration the interactions between our bodies, our environment, our abilities, experiences and intentions.</p>
